<item>
            <title>[SPR-197] PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer cann&apos;t work in inner bean</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-197</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer cann&apos;t work in inner bean when top level bean is ok.&lt;br/&gt;
Such as:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;top1&quot; class=&quot;test.TopLevel&quot; init-method=&quot;init&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;property name=&quot;resourceDirectory&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;$&lt;/p&gt;
{webapp.root}/WEB-INF/lib&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
is ok, but&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;top2&quot; class=&quot;test.TopLevel&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;property name=&quot;secend&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;bean class=&quot;test.Secend&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;property name=&quot;sourceXmlPath&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;${webapp.root}
&lt;p&gt;/WEB-INF/lib/test.xml&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
only get &quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{webapp.root}
&lt;p&gt;/WEB-INF/lib/test.xml&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
